OL,5,FEducation Minister Paul Givan has said
OL,6,Fhe will bring an early learning and
OL,7,Fchildcare strategy paper to the
OL,8,FStormont Executive this week.J"The
OL,9,Fdevelopment of an early learning and
OL,10,Fchildcare strategy is a top priority
OL,11,Ffor me as education minister," he
OL,12,Fsaid.J"There is no time to waste and
OL,13,FI'll be bringing an initial paper on
OL,14,Fthis issue to my executive colleagues
OL,15,Flater this week. It is clear that we
OL,16,Fhave much work to do and I am
OL,17,Fdetermined to press ahead at pace."
