OL,5,FThe Assembly debated a Sinn Fein
OL,6,Fmotion calling for the new Stormont
OL,7,FExecutive to work collectively to
OL,8,Fdeliver a strategy which makes high
OL,9,Fquality childcare affordable for all
OL,10,Ffamilies a priority.JCurrently, there
OL,11,Fis no scheme in place for free
OL,12,Fchildcare in Northern Ireland, unlike
OL,13,Fin England where 30 hours of free
OL,14,Fchildcare a week is offered.JOpening
OL,15,Fthe debate, Sinn Fein MLA Nicola
OL,16,FBrogan said progress on adopting a
OL,17,Fchildcare strategy had stalled while
OL,18,Fthe powersharing Executive did not sit
OL,19,Ffor two years.JShe said: "This motion
OL,20,Fcalls on the Executive to work
OL,21,Fcollectively to deliver a strategy
OL,22,Fwhich makes high quality affordable
OL,23,Fchildcare for all families a priority.
OL,24,F"It is clear that childcare is a
